  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cities in Asia develop climate sensitive adaptation plans</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project raised awareness of the effects of climate change, enhanced knowledge and boosted capacities to act in municipalities in India and the Philippines. With the help of the project, researchers worked together with an international network of municipalities and four cities in each of the two countries to identify specific risks associated with climate change, predict future scenarios and develop decision-making aids. This work provided a foundation on which to build municipal climate change adaptation strategies.</narrative>
  </description>
